cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use this harness in academic work or reporting, please cite it
  using the metadata below. The companion dataset of recorded runs
  lives at github.com/truffle-dev/agentlang-index-data and is
  referenced under `references`.
title: AgentLang Index Harness
abstract: >-
  Benchmark harness for the AgentLang Index. Orchestrates one-shot and
  agent-loop runs of large language models against a fixed 20-task
  corpus, scores attempts under identical reference-test conditions
  across five languages (Zero, TypeScript, Rust, Go, Python), and
  stores per-attempt prompts, responses, and verifier output in SQLite
  for later export to the open dataset.
type: software
